    body: "As a 1st-level character, you start with the following equipment, or you can forgo it and spend 75 GP on equipment of your choice.\nExplorer's Pack\n(a) Greataxe or (b) Battleaxe, Shield, and 10 GP\nHandaxe (4)\n15 GP"
